How to be a PRO at CSGO

1. Type "unbindallmousekeyboard" on the console;
2. Now you can control the game with telepathy;
3. Have fun.

I love the features of this game:
- pay to play against spinbot everywhere;
- low matchmaking priority by accounts in all modes (except long matchmaking);
- monotonous operations (battle passes);
- a system of bans for griefing in any mode, from any player (for you, through no fault of your own);
And much more for 10 years...
Jesus bless this game...

