RO : Dau lectii de cs la preturi acceptabile se accepta si: droguri, bautura , bani si femei Cursul va cuprinde o gama larga de tactici cum ar fi: 
-trasul prin perete (asiguram material didactic); 
-bulanul intentionat; 
-dezamorsare bombei cu smoke-ul; 
-aruncare cu efect a flash-ului; 
-tragerea cu awp in functie de conditile meteo; 
Tot aici vei invata sa: 
-injuri si sa faci codat pe toti cei care te omoara; 
-sa dai tot timpul vina pe restul colegilor; 
-cand mori la un duel face to face sa zici:lag/fps! si multe altele... 
La sfarsitul cursului vei fi certificat PGL ( Pokemon Game League)

Such a nice game u can make friends all over the world;
Such a nice game u can show ur skill and make a good kill;
Such a nice game u can enjoy the team cooperation;
But sadly, nothing come true now...
Only left hacking : (

Pros:
-perfect for the mouse and keyboard;
-easy to learn;
-exciting matches;
-diversified maps;
-support for the community;
-fun matches.


Cons:
-need to pay for weapons with skin;
-keys for cases are expensives;
-in competitive matches, some players make everything to win, even kicking players that aren´t playing so well.

In general I recommend a lot this game.
